Sentencas: Low temperature prepared (La-0.8 Sr-0.2)(0.9) MnO3-delta-Y-0.15 Zr-0.85 O-1.93 (LSM-YSZ) nano-composite cathode has high three-phase boundary (TPB) density and shows higher oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) activity than traditional LSM-YSZ cathode at reduced temperatures.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: But the weak connection between cathode and electrolyte due to low sintering temperature restrains the performance of LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A YSZ interlayer, consisted of nanoparticles smaller than 10 nm, is introduced by spinning coating hydrolyzed YSZ sol solution on electrolyte and sintering at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The thickness of the interlayer is about 150 nm.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The YSZ interlayer intimately adheres to the electrolyte and shows obvious agglomeration with LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The power densities of the cell with interlayer are 0.83, 0.46 and 0.21 W/cm 2 under 0.7 V at 80 0, 70 0
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: and 600 degrees C, respectively, which are 36%, 48% and 50% improved than that of original cell.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The interlayer introduction slightly increases the ohmic resistance but significantly decreases the polarization resistance.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The depressed high frequency arcs of impedance spectra suggest that the oxygen incorporation kinetics are enhanced at the boundary of YSZ interlayer and LSM-YSZ nanocomposite cathode, contributing to improved electrochemical performance of the cell with interlayer.
Titulo: LSM-YSZ nano-composite cathode with YSZ interlayer for solid oxide fuel cells
